  "title": "Accounts Assistant (AP) | 2 Months Contract | Up to $2100 | Havelock",
  "description": "<p><strong>💰 Salary: Up to $2,100 per month</strong><br /><strong>🗓️ Contract: 2 Months</strong><br /><strong>⏰ Working Hours: Mon - Fri, 8:45 AM - 6:00 PM</strong><br /><strong>📍 Location: Havelock MRT (Nearest MRT)</strong></p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br />-Verify and process vendor invoices and credit notes, managing any exceptions.<br />-Execute payment runs accurately and on time.<br />-Review and perform supplier statement reconciliations.<br />-Handle general data entry and maintain accurate financial records, both digital and physical.<br />-Assist with any ad-hoc finance and administrative duties as assigned.</p><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />-Minimum <strong>GCE 'O' Level</strong> or equivalent education.<br />-Minimum <strong>1-2 years</strong> of relevant experience as an Accounts Assistant or in a similar AP-focused role.<br />-Strong attention to detail and ability to handle confidential information discreetly.<br />-Proficiency in basic Microsoft Office functions, including <strong>Excel</strong> and Word.</p><p><br /><br /><strong>Note:</strong> Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
